{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-docs-post-js","path":"/disabling-autologin/","webpackCompilationHash":"6b65d65e9eef7ebf7e30","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"7d735f5e-4a58-5299-8551-fec6de46bed2","html":"<p>You can disable the automatic login process and force JXOS to display the login message at terminal by disabling the <code class=\"language-text\">NoDM</code> systemd service:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> systemctl disable nodm</code></pre></div>\n<p>and to re-enable it again :</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> dpkg-reconfigure nodm</code></pre></div>\n<p>to completely remove it :</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">sudo apt remove nodm</code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Disable AutoLogin"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/disabling-autologin/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/jxminer-config/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Configuring JXMiner"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/installation-liveiso/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"LiveISO Installation"}}}}}